#. <section class="sutta" id="sn16.8"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn16.8:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 16"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn16.8:0.2"
msgid "1. Kassapavagga"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn16.8:0.3"
msgid "8. Tatiyaovādasutta"
msgstr ""

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
#. VAR: kalandakanivāpe → sāvatthiyaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "sn16.8:1.1"
msgid "Rājagahe kalandakanivāpe."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn16.8:1.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā mahākassapo yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho āyasmantaṃ "
"mahākassapaṃ bhagavā etadavoca:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn16.8:1.3"
msgid "“ovada, kassapa, bhikkhū;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn16.8:1.4"
msgid "karohi, kassapa, bhikkhūnaṃ dhammiṃ kathaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn16.8:1.5"
msgid "Ahaṃ vā, kassapa, bhikkhūnaṃ ovadeyyaṃ tvaṃ vā;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn16.8:1.6"
msgid "ahaṃ vā bhikkhūnaṃ dhammiṃ kathaṃ kareyyaṃ tvaṃ vā”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.209"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn16.8:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Dubbacā kho, bhante, etarahi bhikkhū, dovacassakaraṇehi dhammehi "
"samannāgatā, akkhamā, appadakkhiṇaggāhino anusāsanin”ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn16.8:2.2"
msgid ""
"“Tathā hi pana, kassapa, pubbe therā bhikkhū āraññikā ceva ahesuṃ "
"āraññikattassa ca vaṇṇavādino, piṇḍapātikā ceva ahesuṃ piṇḍapātikattassa ca "
"vaṇṇavādino, paṃsukūlikā ceva ahesuṃ paṃsukūlikattassa ca vaṇṇavādino, "
"tecīvarikā ceva ahesuṃ tecīvarikattassa ca vaṇṇavādino, appicchā ceva ahesuṃ "
"appicchatāya ca vaṇṇavādino, santuṭṭhā ceva ahesuṃ santuṭṭhiyā ca "
"vaṇṇavādino, pavivittā ceva ahesuṃ pavivekassa ca vaṇṇavādino, asaṃsaṭṭhā "
"ceva ahesuṃ asaṃsaggassa ca vaṇṇavādino, āraddhavīriyā ceva ahesuṃ "
"vīriyārambhassa ca vaṇṇavādino."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn16.8:3.1"
msgid ""
"Tatra yo hoti bhikkhu āraññiko ceva āraññikattassa ca vaṇṇavādī, piṇḍapātiko "
"ceva piṇḍapātikattassa ca vaṇṇavādī, paṃsukūliko ceva paṃsukūlikattassa ca "
"vaṇṇavādī, tecīvariko ceva tecīvarikattassa ca vaṇṇavādī, appiccho ceva "
"appicchatāya ca vaṇṇavādī, santuṭṭho ceva santuṭṭhiyā ca vaṇṇavādī, "
"pavivitto ceva pavivekassa ca vaṇṇavādī, asaṃsaṭṭho ceva asaṃsaggassa ca "
"vaṇṇavādī, āraddhavīriyo ceva vīriyārambhassa ca vaṇṇavādī, taṃ therā "
"bhikkhū āsanena nimantenti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn16.8:3.2"
msgid ""
"‘ehi, bhikkhu, ko nāmāyaṃ bhikkhu, bhaddako vatāyaṃ bhikkhu, sikkhākāmo "
"vatāyaṃ bhikkhu; ehi, bhikkhu, idaṃ āsanaṃ nisīdāhī’ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn16.8:4.1"
msgid "Tatra, kassapa, navānaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ evaṃ hoti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn16.8:4.2"
msgid ""
"‘yo kira so hoti bhikkhu āraññiko ceva āraññikattassa ca vaṇṇavādī, "
"piṇḍapātiko ceva … pe … paṃsukūliko ceva … tecīvariko ceva … appiccho ceva … "
"santuṭṭho ceva … pavivitto ceva … asaṃsaṭṭho ceva … āraddhavīriyo ceva "
"vīriyārambhassa ca vaṇṇavādī, taṃ therā bhikkhū āsanena nimantenti—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn16.8:4.3"
msgid ""
"ehi, bhikkhu, ko nāmāyaṃ bhikkhu, bhaddako vatāyaṃ bhikkhu, sikkhākāmo "
"vatāyaṃ bhikkhu; ehi, bhikkhu, idaṃ āsanaṃ nisīdāhī’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn16.8:4.4"
msgid "Te tathattāya paṭipajjanti;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn16.8:4.5"
msgid "tesaṃ taṃ hoti dīgharattaṃ hitāya sukhāya."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.210"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn16.8:5.1"
msgid ""
"Etarahi pana, kassapa, therā bhikkhū na ceva āraññikā na ca āraññikattassa "
"vaṇṇavādino, na ceva piṇḍapātikā na ca piṇḍapātikattassa vaṇṇavādino, na "
"ceva paṃsukūlikā na ca paṃsukūlikattassa vaṇṇavādino, na ceva tecīvarikā na "
"ca tecīvarikattassa vaṇṇavādino, na ceva appicchā na ca appicchatāya "
"vaṇṇavādino, na ceva santuṭṭhā na ca santuṭṭhiyā vaṇṇavādino, na ceva "
"pavivittā na ca pavivekassa vaṇṇavādino, na ceva asaṃsaṭṭhā na ca "
"asaṃsaggassa vaṇṇavādino, na ceva āraddhavīriyā na ca vīriyārambhassa "
"vaṇṇavādino."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "sn16.8:6.1"
msgid ""
"Tatra yo hoti bhikkhu ñāto yasassī lābhī "
"cīvarapiṇḍapātasenāsanagilānappaccayabhesajjaparikkhārānaṃ taṃ therā bhikkhū "
"āsanena nimantenti:"
msgstr ""

# BB follows comm in translating as “keen on the company of his brothers in the holy life”. (Sabrahmacārikāmoti ‘‘ime maṃ parivāretvā carantū’’ti evaṃ kāmeti) But it seems to me that the sense of the text doesn’t require such expansion. The point is that they’re trying to butter him up so he’ll share his stuff.
msgctxt "sn16.8:6.2"
msgid ""
"‘ehi, bhikkhu, ko nāmāyaṃ bhikkhu, bhaddako vatāyaṃ bhikkhu, "
"sabrahmacārikāmo vatāyaṃ bhikkhu; ehi, bhikkhu, idaṃ āsanaṃ nisīdāhī’ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "sn16.8:7.1"
msgid "Tatra, kassapa, navānaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ evaṃ hoti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn16.8:7.2"
msgid ""
"‘yo kira so hoti bhikkhu ñāto yasassī lābhī "
"cīvarapiṇḍapātasenāsanagilānappaccayabhesajjaparikkhārānaṃ taṃ therā bhikkhū "
"āsanena nimantenti—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn16.8:7.3"
msgid ""
"ehi, bhikkhu, ko nāmāyaṃ bhikkhu, bhaddako vatāyaṃ bhikkhu, sabrahmacārikāmo "
"vatāyaṃ bhikkhu; ehi, bhikkhu, idaṃ āsanaṃ nisīdāhī’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn16.8:7.4"
msgid "Te tathattāya paṭipajjanti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn16.8:7.5"
msgid "Tesaṃ taṃ hoti dīgharattaṃ ahitāya dukkhāya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn16.8:7.6"
msgid "Yañhi taṃ, kassapa, sammā vadamāno vadeyya:"
msgstr ""

#. VAR: abhipatthanā → abhibhavanā (bj, pts1-2) | abhivānā (s1-3)
#. VAR: brahmacāriabhipatthanenā’ti → brahmacārābhibhavanenāti (bj, pts1-2) | brahmacārābhivānenāti (s1-3)
msgctxt "sn16.8:7.7"
msgid ""
"‘upaddutā brahmacārī brahmacārūpaddavena abhipatthanā brahmacārī "
"brahmacāriabhipatthanenā’ti, etarahi taṃ, kassapa, sammā vadamāno vadeyya: ‘"
"upaddutā brahmacārī brahmacārūpaddavena abhipatthanā brahmacārī "
"brahmacāriabhipatthanenā’”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn16.8:7.8"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
